en_52593_0	Opposition Leader Ranil Wickremesinghe has challenged the government to go in for a referendum in a bid to ascertain if the people of the country would approve of the current regime & its administration.
en_52593_1	Wickremesinghe issued this challenge while addressing the Galle District United National Party propaganda member's programme which was held this morning.
en_52593_2	Speaking here Opposition Leader Ranil Wickremesinghe expressed these views.
